        <updateDate>2009-01-22T20:08:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Nationwide Freight and Personal Mobility Act - Specifies a formula for the automatic authorization of additional appropriations for National Highway System (NHS) improvement projects, starting FY2010, if apportionments fall below a certain level.</p> <p>Revises the federal share of non-Interstate highway projects to make it: (1) 80% for non-NHS projects; and (2) 85% for NHS projects.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
